{"tid":1136751,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴賽後稱讚美斯：足球之神；不可思議的球員","createTime":"2019-05-03T08:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T20:55:51.000Z","uid":28938,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dfb7ebebcb40f6c8f9f1570d1fe0386d1e134cbd","tid":1136751,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:28:56.000Z","msg":"在歐聯半決賽首回合比賽結束後，摩連奴也加入了美吹大軍，他稱讚美斯為&ldquo;足球之神(God of football)&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n在點評巴塞與利物浦的比賽中，摩連奴説到：&ldquo;利物浦的表現足夠勇敢，很難想象過去20年中有人可以在歐聯比賽中從控球率方面戰勝巴塞。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;但足球之神讓比賽完全不同。儘管巴塞有着很強大的整體，現象級的球員，但那個球員(美斯)是完全不可思議的一個。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;利物浦本值得一個更好的結果，但最後的角球本可以使比分變成4-0或者5-0，因為場上平衡一旦被打破，他們就很難應對了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;現在的問題是，當美斯決定離開的時候，巴塞會變成什麼樣子。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"6739a1539f7e2bc233f6cf9adc6f0d0c4f0151e3","tid":1136751,"uid":16468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d879de9d98b1131f648fe100fbce531c056dd6","tid":1136751,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:30:22.000Z","msg":"Nineup"},{"pid":"37e67971c89beb7e3fa46860ea8b42fb25ee9d6f","tid":1136751,"uid":33527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:31:04.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩今次貼正常新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f691dfc7eb51caacb0ada48ff2b5fe8d1101d3e","tid":1136751,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T20:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}